    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc_jc.00394_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Camden</name>
                    <date when="1888-08-12">Sunday Evn'g</date>
                    <date when="1888-08-12">Aug: 12 '88<ptr target="loc.03866_n1"/></date>
                </dateline>
                <salute/>
            </opener>

            <p>Nothing very new or different&#8212;I am still in my sick room&#8212;Sit up most of the
                day&#8212;write some &#38; keep pretty good spirits&#8212;but am as weak &#38; feeble as ever.
                (Sometimes I opine will remain so.) I think Herbert<ptr target="prc.00084_n3"/> is coming to America soon&#8212;may
                be this month. It is raining all day like fury&#8212;coolish&#8212;</p>

            <closer>
                <salute/>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc_jc.00393_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
        </body>
